"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-news-world-olympic-paris-2024-jackson-james-jj-rice-tonga-death-b1164917.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News|World  A rising athlete has died in a tragic diving accident just weeks before his debut at theOlympicsinParis.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jackson James Rice, 18, was in line to become the first Caucasian to represent Tonga at the Games, having qualified for the new kite-foiling event.\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Rice_(writer)\", \"score\": 0.9730803580613707, \"rank\": 0.02764976958524251, \"text\": \"James Rice\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Rice_(writer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Rice_(writer)\"}, {\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"score\": 0.999358298142889, \"rank\": 0.0006396701989371911, \"text\": \"Caucasian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\"}, {\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"score\": 0.9999999955166459, \"rank\": 4.483301377932514e-09, \"text\": \"Tonga\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His father Darren confirmed the devastating news of his son's death to the Matangi Tonga newspaper.\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matangi_Tonga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4815621432596477e-20, \"text\": \"Matangi Tonga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matangi_Tonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matangi_Tonga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The teenager, known as JJ Rice, died on Saturday from a \\\"suspected shallow water blackout\\\".\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Good_Times\", \"score\": 0.8408673894152257, \"rank\": 0.17746225273069116, \"text\": \"JJ\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Good_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Good_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had been free-diving when his body was found beneath a boat at 12.15pm, with subsequent resuscitation attempts unsuccessful.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jackson, who hadBritishparents Darren and Nina, was born in the US before moving to Tonga.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9938258862738526, \"rank\": 0.006212386490254838, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 861, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nina_Girado\", \"score\": 0.9997597813028305, \"rank\": 0.00024010376648522113, \"text\": \"Nina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nina_Girado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nina_Girado\"}, {\"begin\": 883, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8687031526102932, \"rank\": 0.15113147177836175, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"score\": 0.9999999955166459, \"rank\": 4.483301377932514e-09, \"text\": \"Tonga\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He grew up in Ha\\u02bbapai - where his parents run a tourist lodge - and viewed himself as Tongan.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"score\": 0.9999899116009622, \"rank\": 1.0058909186874836e-05, \"text\": \"Tongan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jackson's sister Lily paid tribute on social media, writing in a Facebook post: \\\"I was blessed with the most amazing brother in the whole world and it pains me to say that he's passed away.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9938258862738526, \"rank\": 0.006212386490254838, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was an amazing kite foiler and he would have made it to the Olympics and come out with a big shiny medal \\u2026 he made so many amazing friends all over the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The talented athlete qualified for what had been due to be his first Olympic Games last December, courtesy of an eight-placed finish at a Sail Sydney event.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1505, \"end\": 1511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9578760423065035, \"rank\": 0.04397633338204338, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kite foil racing combines aspects of \\\"sailing, wakeboarding, windsurfing, surfing and paragliding into one extreme sport\\\".\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Rice remembered how aged 15, Jackson risked his life to help save some of the 18 passengers on a ferryboat which capsized in choppy seas off Faleloa in 2021.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9938258862738526, \"rank\": 0.006212386490254838, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 1788, \"end\": 1795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faleloa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Faleloa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faleloa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faleloa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On another occasion, Jackson rescued two girls who had been swept off a sandbar, pulling them back to safety.\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1834, \"title\": \"http://dbped